ces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了"},{"pid":"5fa3f2e1f1c304e7c81265bdb35aab57fb7a79fe","tid":631263,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de621fa1d0ba7c7a1e96fda851a49469c791cc9e","tid":631263,"uid":9247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:43:04.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:07:08.000Z","msg":"收la"},{"pid":"43ff0c0ffe545e6c8d9641c05a921460fd7dc9d8","tid":631263,"uid":96007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"無論畫構圖角色設計都好有吸力"},{"pid":"125ff3e273cd8701f2b08d7061ee21d21affb108","tid":631263,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:24:29.000Z","msg":"清仲有冇漫畫推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dfa88475fc56ac8950d7c881bd94a69b4365b6","tid":631263,"uid":52073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"125ff3e273cd8701f2b08d7061ee21d21affb108","tid":631263,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:24:29.000Z","msg":"清仲有冇漫畫推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"雖然睇過好多漫 但好多都唔記得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推介既話就魂環,聲之形 呢2套基本上係我必推既神作 不過應該大把人睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個人黎講最鐘意既係hxh,jojo,最強會長黑神 頭2套應該唔洗我多講 黑神就因為岩我電波 而且入面某個角色真係造得好好 上面三套都係衝擊到我既漫畫 所以我好愛佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而個人覺得既佳作有<br />\n魔偶馬戲團(比較慢熱 不過中期d線合埋一齊真係好正好睇,不過我未睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n少女不十分(唔講咁多 好睇 有輕小說 )<br />\n<br />\n空知英秋既十三(短篇黎 幾好睇 有笑有淚 )<br />\n<br />\n七大罪(聲評2極化 缺點係強弱設定有問題但文戲十分好睇畫功又十分傳神 完美咁表達到人物既感情,打鬥方面更係爽快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n家教(聲評又係2極化 而且強弱設定比上面果套幾加離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且仲要on9爛尾 但因為人設真係好型好有魅力 而且某d篇章好好睇  所以推)<br />\n<br />\n美食獵人(節奏快,打鬥爽 劇情完全唔拖)<br />\n<br />\n魔法小神童加旋(有笑有淚 一套唔錯的作品)<br />\n<br />\n無聊可以睇下既有<br />\n元魔子(比較慢熱 冇乜高潮位 但畫功幾好 可以一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n螺旋卷鉤生(畫風獵奇?總知就係一看難忘既感覺)<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥破壞學園(早排見到有人開post討論<br />\n劇情鋪排得好 又冇乜不合理既情節都幾有趣)<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係西尾維新既作品 因為我好鐘意條友所以推介 如果岩電波既就會覺得好睇 唔係既話就會有on9 中二病既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想入門既可以睇左箱入少女同埋上面推行既少女不十分先<br />\n其實仲有好多好睇 不過一時之間唔記得 諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e6db3c2773c9a0274f23986cd8744b0bf4c4ad","tid":631263,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43ff0c0ffe545e6c8d9641c05a921460fd7dc9d8","tid":631263,"uid":96007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"無論畫構圖角色設計都好有吸力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:58:41.000Z","msg":"ching識貨"},{"pid":"e039eb0783de17d165c6e78ba537df55687ecde4","tid":631263,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T04:51:17.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"8865e800a9d5b334bde4885344a4002fa37c0e45","tid":631263,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:58:12.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"fe0193d8907d5ed8fe3be10666646c8282dec535","tid":631263,"uid":52423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T14:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/220659_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F220659_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=e01eba85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/220704_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" da